Name: Space Force
About the game: Space Force is a simple arcade game. You're pilot of a space ship. Your goal is, you have to dodge all the blocks and go as much as you can. If you hit you'll lose. Get double points, speed up the time or slow it down. Set new highscores, get more credits and buy new spaceships! Enjoy the ride and have a safe flights! Features Fun Arcade Gameplay 5 Different Spaceships Infinite Level Design Power-ups HD Effects
